Master Assassin
The Master Assassin is a professional killer with an extensive repertoire of
combat techniques, poisons, and methods. They are not soldiers; they are
precision instruments for eliminating specific targets. Their services command
enormous fees and their skills are unmatched in single-target elimination.

Master Assassins choose from Espionage, Physical, Rogue, and Weapons skill
categories. They are trained in virtually every form of personal combat and
killing.

Attribute requirements: IQ 12, ME 12, PP 14.
Starting equipment: Two vibro-knives, a concealed laser pistol, dark civilian
clothing, poison kit, restraints, and a substantial credit reserve.
